room_title: Escape room "The Wizarding School" by Quest Factor in Seattle
room_address: 511 Boren Ave N SUITE B Seattle, WA 98109
room_description: The rival houses of The Wizarding School are preparing for the tournament. The night before the game, you realize that someone stole your racing broom! You suspect that your Potions professor could be the orchestrator of this evil plan. Now it's up to you and your team to sneak into his chambers and recover the broom but hurry, he will be back in one hour!
